<plot>Taxi to L.A. which looks at the sense of sight, is a road-movie about Samantha, an impetuous Montréal socialite who embarks on a cross-country journey to Los Angeles. Grief-stricken after her fiance calls off their wedding, Sam impulsively hires Jack, a taxi driver with voyeuristic tendencies, to drive her from Montréal to L.A. Can a relationship between them last beyond their eight-day taxi ride to L.A.?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?532409</url></doc>
